window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>Three billionaire night club owners with a tragic past find the women they can’t live without.</b></p> <p><b><i>More than Sexy</i></b><b>: </b></p> <p>Jason Dare’s long-awaited story!</p> <p>One protective alpha male....</p> <p>Plus one hot curvy blonde....</p> <p>Equals an insta-love they can’t deny. </p> <p><b><i>Twice as Sexy</i></b><b>: </b></p> <p>He’s the bad boy her mother warned her about.</p> <p>The guy who makes her crave all the naughty things a good girl shouldn’t want.</p> <p><b><i>Better than Sexy</i></b><b>:</b></p> <p>Insta-love only happens in the movies.</p> <p>Insta-lust? That she’d buy into.</p> <p>Until she meets take-charge club owner Landon Bennett and falls head over heels at a glance.</p>"; 
